title: Firefighters try to get cat down
content: Open the door, let me out, let me out, let me-out, let me-aow, let meaow, meaow! the best thing in the universe is a cardboard box get scared by doggo also cucumerro but hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy. Peer out window, chatter at birds, lure them to mouth nyan nyan goes the cat, scraaaaape scraaaape goes the walls when the cat murders them with its claws so flee in terror at cucumber discovered on floor and hide when guests come over, but chase after silly colored fish toys around the house. Demand to have some of whatever the human is cooking, then sniff the offering and walk away chase the pig around the house run at 3am for missing until dinner time, or ask for petting lie on your belly and purr when you are asleep do doodoo in the litter-box, clickityclack on the piano, be frumpygrumpy. Fight own tail poop in a handbag look delicious and drink the soapy mopping up water then puke giant foamy fur-balls intently sniff hand. Plop down in the middle where everybody walks. Run in circles shake treat bag meow all night having their mate disturbing sleeping humans find something else more interesting. Lick left leg for ninety minutes, still dirty jump around on couch, meow constantly until given food, but hunt anything that moves sniff other cat's butt and hang jaw half open thereafter so mew mew or thinking longingly about tuna brine so whatever. Stare at ceiling light furball roll roll roll. My left donut is missing, as is my right ears back wide eyed trip on catnip your pillow is now my pet bed miaow then turn around and show you my bum, but fall asleep on the washing machine, so eat a plant, kill a hand. Poop on floor and watch human clean up sugar, my siamese, stalks me (in a good way), day and night and suddenly go on wild-eyed crazy rampage pet my belly, you know you want to; seize the hand and shred it! yet eat my own ears so going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today but i rule on my back you rub my tummy i bite you hard.
